  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single arm dose escalation study of recombinant human keratinocyte growth factor
      given to patients undergoing allogeneic bone marrow transplantation who are at high risk for
      graft versus host disease (GVHD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
